    "description": {
      "value": "<h3><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"> Confabulation powder</h3><p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Alchemy Manual pg. 11</em></p><p><strong>Price</strong> 80 gp; <strong>Weight</strong> 0</p><p><strong>Type</strong> inhaled; <strong>Save</strong> Fortitude DC 18</p><p><strong>Frequency</strong> 1/minute for 2 minutes</p><p><strong>Initial Effect</strong> staggered for 1 minute; <strong>Secondary Effect</strong> If already staggered, stunned, or unconscious, the victim becomes highly suggestible. If an event (whether true or false) is described to him, he unconsciously fabricates a detailed memory of the event, filling in any gaps in the description with his own best guesses. The confabulated memory can be disbelieved with a successful DC 18 Will save the first time it is recalled, but if the save fails, the victim treats it as completely genuine thereafter. All confabulated memories can be removed with a <em>restoration </em>or <em>heal </em>spell</p><p><strong>Cure</strong> 1 save</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Alchemical Recipe<h3><p><strong>Recipe</strong> (20 quicksilver + 15 cytillesh spores)/digestion; <strong>Craft</strong> DC 18</p><p><strong>Time</strong> 1 day; <strong>Tools</strong> heat source; <strong>Type</strong> poison</p>",
